title: Totem's Realm
description: In a crazy turn of events, Sera, an office worker, is stranded on a remote island and captured by a native tribe. A mysterious Tarzan-esque man rescues her, but it turns out he’s also on the run. As they flee the tribes that are after them, Sera develops a special power she can’t quite understand. She also feels attracted to the strange man...
author: SOOHYEON
